Privacy Policy

Mafia Game does not collect, store, or share any personal data from users.

All game data such as player names are stored locally on the user's device and are not transmitted to any external servers.

The app may use basic system permissions required for normal operation.

We do not use tracking technologies, analytics, or third-party data collection services.

If any features are added in the future that involve data collection, this policy will be updated accordingly.

